\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15024670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Could you tell me your year of marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13070006 NB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Yes, 1924.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15024670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Could you tell me your year of birth and where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13070006 NB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Yes, October the twelfth and I was born at Lat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid208827\charrsid15539754 ch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 ington. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Essex{\*\xmlclose}.
