Oh well, yes, sometimes, I know we - once we had a horrible - a horrible spider with wiggly legs. You know, stringy legs and that went like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15024670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Did you have a toy each at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13070006 NB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Yes. Yes, we were all served the same. I don't say we had the same thing, but we all had a - we all had a - equal to it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15024670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13070006 NB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 My father could play a - an }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8084273\charrsid15539754 accordion}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
