s the way here, she - we were going to school then, I don't know how she managed to get it but she got a Jews Harp. And I don't know how we managed to get hold of this Jews Harp but he - he could play it, he played - he played that beautiful. He didn't - 
he didn't even - he didn't even tell her where he got that - it was hers but he didn't even tell her where he - where he got the Jews Harp from but that was hers. So we used to have that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15024670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13070006 NB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5537365\charrsid15539754 Well no. I m
ean, some of 'em weren't - big enough to really - no, not make too much on the - well - only about the only time we had was a bit of paper and a comb.
